[PLAYING PIANO]

00:31:42.390 --> 00:31:45.110
PJ MORTON: All right,
so if you know this one,

00:31:45.110 --> 00:31:46.790
I want you all to help me.

00:31:46.790 --> 00:31:48.350
I did a cover on this album.

00:31:51.550 --> 00:31:55.540
I looked up the top
10 songs of all time

00:31:55.540 --> 00:31:58.650
and one of my favorites
just happened to be there.

00:31:58.650 --> 00:32:00.760
It's How Deep Is Your
Love by the Bee Gees.

00:32:04.190 --> 00:32:05.530
Are they from Austrailia?

00:32:05.530 --> 00:32:07.010
Yeah, I think.

00:32:07.010 --> 00:32:09.250
Aussies, they had
some soul in there.

00:32:09.250 --> 00:32:10.670
I felt the soul in there.

00:32:10.670 --> 00:32:16.050
But I'm like, I think I can
fully put the soul in it.

00:32:16.050 --> 00:32:19.710
So I redid it, and I'm going
to do that one right now.

00:32:19.710 --> 00:32:21.792
