00:32:26.632 --> 00:35:08.932
[PJ MORTON SINGING "HOW DEEP IS
 YOUR LOVE"]

00:35:08.932 --> 00:35:10.310
Thank you all so much, man.

00:35:10.310 --> 00:35:12.110
[APPLAUSE]

00:35:16.610 --> 00:35:19.360
PEGAH HAGHIGHAT:
Thank you so much, PJ.

